const { Shape, HexagonalGrid, HexagonalTile, Search } = Gridy const grid = new HexagonalGrid(70, true, Shape.Rhombus, 4, 4) const search = new Search( new HexagonalTile(), Infinity, 8, undefined, grid.tiles ) const path = search.path(grid.tile(3, 3)) return { grid, showTiles: true, path, showCoordinates: true }

Connectionsdemo

Code
const { Shape, HexagonalGrid, connections } = Gridy const size = 11 const grid = new HexagonalGrid(24, true, Shape.Rhombus, size, size) const highlight = grid.tiles.filter((s, i) => ((s.x - s.y) % 3) || !((i + s.x) % 8)) const lines = connections(highlight).filter((l) => l.length === 5) return { grid, lines, highlight, showTiles: true }
